    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Meanwhile, bash your <strong>Fable pulled mushrooms</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> to break them up</p><p>Zest your <strong>lime[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1681892879783-x200.jpg",
