            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s] </strong>thinly</p><p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage</strong> <strong>slaw mix</strong> to a bowl with<strong> </strong>the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>zested lime[s]</strong>, <strong>chopped spring onion</strong>, <strong>mayo </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>lime slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1681892906533-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1681892906533-x400.jpg",
