            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Finely dice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>diced tomato</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>remaining lime zest</strong>, a squeeze of <strong>lime juice</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix it all together – this is your<strong> salsa</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
