      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chipotle pulled mushrooms </strong>with the <strong>cooked rice</strong>,<strong> lime slaw </strong>and <strong>salsa </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
